name: louisiana-speaks-regional-plan-community-growth-options-vacant-developed-and-constrained-areas-
notes: This GIS raster data set illustrates vacant, developed, and constrained areas for the 35 parishes in the Louisiana Speaks Regional Plan South Louisiana study area. The data set combines environmental or physical constraints (open water, wetland or marsh, and steep slopes) with committed land (parks and civic or institutional land) from various data sources.
